𝙚𝙭𝙖𝙢𝙥𝙡𝙚 2
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
int i = 0;    // initialization expression
while (i < 5)   // test expression
{
cout << "Good morning\n";
i++;    // update expression
}
return 0;
}
𝙙𝙤 𝙬𝙝𝙞𝙡𝙚 𝙡𝙤𝙤𝙥
